(!begin_liste) [Availability]

!item [Name:]
¯Inquire current fill area attributes® - Obtain the attributes for filling area

!item [Opcode:]
37

!item [Syntax:]
void vqf_attributes ( int16_t handle, int16_t *attrib );

!item [Description:]
The call vqf_attributes reports back the current attributes for filled graphic
objects.

!begin_xlist !short [Parameter]
!item [Parameter]
Meaning
!item [~]
~
!item [handle]
Workstation identifier
!item [attrib[0!]]
Fill type
!item [attrib[1!]]
Fill colour
!item [attrib[2!]]
Fill style index
!item [attrib[3!]]
Writing mode
!item [attrib[4!]]
Perimeter flag:
!begin_table [rl]
0 = !! invisible
<> 0 = !! visible
!end_table
!end_xlist

!item [(!nolink [Return]) value:]
The function does not return a result.

!item [Availability:]
Supported by all devices.

!item [Group:]
Inquire functions

!item [See also:]
(!link [Binding] [Bindings for vqf_attributes]) ~ vswr_mode ~ vs_color ~ vsf_interior ~
vsf_style ~ vsf_color ~ vsf_perimeter
               
(!ende_liste)
